six = function(v){
  if(anyNA(v)){
    for (i in 1:length(v)) {
      if(is.na(v[i])){
        v[i]=mean(v,na.rm = TRUE)
      }
      else{
        v[i]=v[i]
      }
    }
    return(v)
      }
  else{
    print("There is no missing value")
    return(v)
  }
}

Mode = function(x){
    ta = table(x)
    tam = max(ta)
    if (all(ta == tam))
         mod = NA
    else
         if(is.numeric(x))
    mod = as.numeric(names(ta)[ta == tam])
    else
         mod = names(ta)[ta == tam]
    return(mod)
}
seven = function(v){
  if(anyNA(v)){
    for (i in 1:length(v)) {
      if(is.na(v[i])){
        v[i]=Mode(v)
      }
      else{
        v[i]=v[i]
      }
    }
    return(v)
      }
  else{
    print("There is no missing value")
    return(v)
  }
}

eight=function(d)
{
  for(i in 1:ncol(d)){
    if(is.numeric(d[[i]])){
      d[[i]]=six(d[[i]])
    }
    if(is.character(d[[i]])){
      d[[i]]=seven(d[[i]])
    }
  }
  return(d)
}

#forest

set.seed(1234)
splitIndex = createDataPartition(Hospital3$EMG, p = .70, list=FALSE)
train= Hospital3[splitIndex,]
test = Hospital3[-splitIndex,]

myGrid = expand.grid(maxdepth = c(1:10))

model= train(EMG~.,data=train, method = "rpart2",tuneGrid = myGrid)

print(model)
